external_knowledge:
- "nests" refers to the location of the airport in a state;
- "unique identifiers" refers to the `airport_code`;
- "frequented by carriers" refers to the `airline_name` in the `airlines` table;
- "avoid the label of 'Express'" means the `airline_name` does not contain the word "Express";
- "more than one presence in the records" means `COUNT(T1.airport_id) > 1`.
